{"_path":"/maps/_workflow/compiler/compiler","_dir":"compiler","_draft":false,"_partial":true,"_locale":"","title":"Compiler","description":"编译器原理与实践，重点介绍 Babel 等前端编译工具的工作原理和使用方法。","original_path":"/_workflow/compiler.md","body":{"type":"root","children":[{"type":"element","tag":"h2","props":{"id":"babel"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Babel"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h4","props":{"id":"babel-是什么工作原理是怎样的"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"babel 是什么？工作原理是怎样的？"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Babel 主要的作用是转换与编译，能够将新标准中前沿的代码技术转换为相同（或类似）功能的代码，使其能够在旧的浏览器中运行。babel 使用 Babylon（Babel-parser） 将代码解析为 AST，使用 babel-traverse 维护 AST 的状态，做一些源码级别的转换，最后使用 babel-generator 读取 AST 并生成代码。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h2","props":{"id":"现代编译工具"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"现代编译工具"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h4","props":{"id":"swc-相比-babel-的性能优势"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"SWC 相比 Babel 的性能优势"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"ul","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Rust 实现"}]},{"type":"text","value":"：SWC 使用 Rust 编写，编译为原生代码，无 JavaScript 运行时开销"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"并行处理"}]},{"type":"text","value":"：SWC 利用多核 CPU 并行处理文件，Babel 单线程执行"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"速度提升"}]},{"type":"text","value":"：大型项目构建速度可提升 10-20 倍"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"兼容性"}]},{"type":"text","value":"：SWC 支持 Babel 的大部分插件生态，可作为 drop-in 替代"}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h4","props":{"id":"esbuild-的-go-实现带来的构建速度提升"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"esbuild 的 Go 实现带来的构建速度提升"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"ul","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Go 语言优势"}]},{"type":"text","value":"：esbuild 使用 Go 编写，编译为单个静态二进制文件，启动极快"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"极致性能"}]},{"type":"text","value":"：比 Webpack 快 10-100 倍，比 Babel 快 10-30 倍"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"内置功能"}]},{"type":"text","value":"：TypeScript、JSX、代码压缩等原生支持，无需额外 loader"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"局限性"}]},{"type":"text","value":"：插件生态不如 Webpack 丰富，复杂场景可能需要配合其他工具"}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h4","props":{"id":"什么时候还需要-babel"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"什么时候还需要 Babel？"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"ul","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"复杂转换需求"}]},{"type":"text","value":"：需要自定义 AST 转换逻辑时，Babel 的插件生态更丰富"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"遗留项目"}]},{"type":"text","value":"：已有大量 Babel 配置和插件，迁移成本较高"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"特定插件依赖"}]},{"type":"text","value":"：某些特定场景只有 Babel 插件支持"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"调试需求"}]},{"type":"text","value":"：Babel 的转换过程更易理解和调试"}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h2","props":{"id":"资源"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"资源"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"ul","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"eleme